    "My training allows me to understand and explain complex topics like retirement planning, portfolio diversification, tax-efficient investing, risk management, and more.Think of me as a digital tool built to provide clear, balanced, and up-to-date financial insights -similar to how a seasoned advisor would draw from years of education (like CFP or CFA credentials) and client experience.",
    "I stay current with market trends, economic data, and financial regulations, so I can offer guidance that aligns with today's best practices.That said, while I can help you explore options and understand concepts, it's always wise to consult a licensed financial professional for personalized advice --especially when it comes to your unique financial situation and long-term goals.Would you like help with a specific financial planning topic?",
